harvard industries <hava> announces stock split
    st. louis, march 31 - 
harvard industries inc said its board approved a two-for-one stock
split in the form of a special stock dividend of its outstanding
common stock. the special dividend is payable may 28, 1987, to
stockholders of record april 24, 1987. the split will be effected by
one additional share for each common share held, the company said.
